::Reptilica/Bloodystrike::

Reptilica stops yelling as he feels Desmonus' body sprawled over his 
stomach, his hands unconsciously sliding to her sides, forgetting 
about the wall that was rushing up at them. Bloodystrike hit the wall 
first, followed by Reptilica crashing into him, still holding 
Desmonus.

Bloodystrike groans, moving to get Reptilica's foot out of his face.
